values:
I hate those stupid T-Shirts that are suppossed to be witty. Like: "North Korea's got Seoul" or like "Cinco de mayo" And then there are five cans of mayonaise. Wow, witty, cool. You're so individualistic that you buy a shirt with a saying you didn't make up yourself.

Anyone who wears these shirts are automatically minused 10 points on my respect level.

Lmfao I actually like the camoflauge "HA! Now you can't see me!" I'm so ghetto hahahah
